original: Bengtsson, Nils Pål Folke, chefre-raktör, Jönköping, f. 23/12/98 i Kul-lings-Skövde, Älvsb. L, av riksd :man-nen o. lantbr. Emil B. o. Gottfrida Nilsson. — Tvåår. folkhögsk. i Stenstorp o. AxvaW. Res. t. Finl. 43. Anst. i Smålandsbygdens Tidn. 27, chefred, där fr. 44. Siign.: Exman, F, B.
translated: Bengtsson, Nils Pål Folke, chief editor, Jönköping, born December 23rd, 1898 in Kullings-Skövde, Älvsborg County, son of the Member of Parliament and farmer Emil B. and Gottfrida Nilsson. Attended a two-year folk high school in Stenstorp and Axvall. Traveled to Finland in 1943. Employed at Smålandsbygdens Tidning in 1927 and became chief editor from 1944. Married, but the name of the partner is not mentioned.
